org.jsfml.system

Class Time

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jsfml.system.Time
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<Time>

    public final class Time
extends Object
implements Comparable<Time>, Serializable
    Represents a time period and provides functionality to convert between various time units, as well as arithmetic operations on time intervals.
    See Also:
